These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-1::.
There 4 different types of food: avocado, peas, pomegranate, kale
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, ice-hockey, soccer, weightlifting
1. the person eating avocado is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1
2. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the far left##1
3. the person who's sport is soccer is between the person who's sport is ice-hockey and the person eating peas##2
4. the person eating kale is on the far left##1
5. the person eating pomegranate is between the person eating peas and the person eating avocado##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |    3     |     4      |
| Food   | kale         | peas   | pomegranate | avocado       |
| Sport      | weightlifting | cycling | soccer   | ice-hockey |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: gardening, magic-tricks, reading, video-games
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: ritmeester, game, pall-mall, tiparillo
1. the tiparillo-smoker is between the person who's hobby is reading and the game-smoker##2
2. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the far right##1
3. the pall-mall-smoker is on the right of the ritmeester-smoker##1
4. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the ritmeester-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |    3    |      4      |
| Hobby         | magic-tricks | gardening | reading | video-games |
| Cigar   | game    | tiparillo   | ritmeester | pall-mall       |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-3::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  architect, paramedic, scientist, teacher
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, british, colombian, french
1. the colombian is on the right of the teacher##1
2. the colombian is between the british and the paramedic##2
3. the british is on the far left##1
4. the french is on the left of the scientist##1
5. the paramedic is the french##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |     4      |
| Job          | teacher    | architect | paramedic   | scientist  |
| Nationality   | british | colombian   | french | australian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-4::.
4 different pets are kept: cat, lizard, pony, rat
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: western, epic, comedy, spy
1. the person watching epic movies is the owner of the lizard##1
2. the owner of the cat is between the person watching western movies and the owner of the rat##2
3. the person watching epic movies is on the far right##1
4. the owner of the cat is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1   |   2    |     3      |    4     |
| Pet     | rat   | cat    | pony       | lizard   |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy | spy | western | epic |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, hot-chocolate, iced-tea, soy-milk
4 different pets are kept: lizard, cat, mouse, rat
1. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
2. the owner of the mouse is on the far left##1
3. the owner of the lizard is on the far right##1
4. the person drinking soy-milk is between the owner of the lizard and the owner of the cat##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1       |    2     |     3     |       4       |
| Beverage   | fanta        | iced-tea | soy-milk  | hot-chocolate |
| Pet      | mouse | cat  | rat | lizard    |

