.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-7::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: electronic, gospel, house, punk
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: surfing, weightlifting, badminton, parkour
1. the fan of gospel is the person who's sport is surfing##1
2. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the person who's sport is surfing##1
3. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the fan of electronic##1
4. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1
5. the fan of electronic is between the person who's sport is surfing and the fan of house##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | punk   | gospel | electronic | house      |
| Sport     | badminton | surfing    | weightlifting  | parkour |

