1. the blend-smoker is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
2. the old-henry-smoker is between the person who's sport is soccer and the game-smoker##2
3. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the far left##1
4. the blend-smoker is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |       2       |     3      |     4      |
| Sport       | biathlon | weightlifting | soccer     | lacrosse   |
| Cigar   | game   | old-henry     | baccarat | blend |

