4 different pets are kept: ferret, hamster, guinea-pig, mouse
1. the librarian is between the owner of the ferret and the dressmaker##2
2. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the dressmaker##1
3. the videographer is on the right of the dressmaker##1
4. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
5. the dressmaker is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |     3      |      4       |
| Job         | entrepreneur | librarian | dressmaker | videographer |
| Pet   | ferret         | mouse       | hamster    | guinea-pig         |

