.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-10::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: lily, bellflower, iris, tulip
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, ice-hockey, swimming, tennis
1. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the right of the person who growstulip##1
2. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the person who growsiris##1
3. the person who growslily is on the right of the person who growsbellflower##1
4. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
5. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is between the person who growsbellflower and the person who's sport is tennis##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |    3     |    4     |
| Flower    | tulip   | iris      | bellflower   | lily  |
| Sport   | tennis | ice-hockey | swimming | baseball |

