.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-11::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: taxi, jet-ski, bike, car
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, fantasy, superhero, time-travel
1. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the person watching fantasy movies##1
2. the person driving the jet-ski is between the person driving the car and the person driving the taxi##2
3. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the person watching superhero movies##1
4. the person watching superhero movies is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3    |      4      |
| Transport          | taxi     | jet-ski | car   | bike        |
| Movie-Genre   | animation | superhero   | fantasy | time-travel |

