.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-12::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: filmmaking, rock-climbing, singing, writing
City: venice, colone, liverpool, london
1. the person traveling to liverpool is the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
2. the person traveling to colone is on the left of the person traveling to london##1
3. the person traveling to venice is the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
4. the person who's hobby is singing is the person traveling to colone##1
5. the person traveling to venice is on the right of the person who's hobby is writing##1
6. the person traveling to colone is between the person who's hobby is rock-climbing and the person who's hobby is writing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |    3    |     4      |
| Hobby         | rock-climbing | singing | writing | filmmaking |
| City   | liverpool          | colone     | london  | venice     |

