2. the person eating avocado is the person driving the scooter##1
3. the person eating nectarine is between the person driving the scooter and the person eating cabbage##2
4. the person eating avocado is on the right of the person eating nectarine##1
5. the person driving the bike is on the left of the person eating cabbage##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2   |   3    |    4     |
| Food   | cauliflower | cabbage | nectarine | avocado |
| Transport     | bike     | bus   | subway | scooter  |

