2. the spanish is the person playing bridge##1
3. the person playing canasta is between the person playing poker and the italian##2
4. the person playing domino is the person playing domino##1
5. the person playing domino is on the right of the person playing bridge##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3     |     4     |
| Nationality   | spanish | italian | egyptian | pakistani |
| Game           | bridge  | domino  | canasta | poker      |

