.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-18::.
4 different games are played: monopoly, whist, bridge, snooker
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, roller, ship, skateboard
1. the person driving the roller is on the right of the person driving the bike##1
2. the person driving the bike is on the far left##1
3. the person playing whist is between the person driving the bike and the person playing bridge##2
4. the person playing snooker is the person driving the bike##1
5. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2    |       3       |     4      |
| Game       | snooker | whist | bridge | monopoly |
| Transport   | bike    | roller  | skateboard    | ship       |

