2. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left of the person playing go##1
3. the polish is the person playing mah-jongg##1
4. the person playing snooker is between the american and the chinese##2
5. the chinese is the person playing whist##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Nationality   | polish   | american   | australian | chinese |
| Game         | mah-jongg | go | snooker     | whist    |

