.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-20::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: d&b, rock, hip-hop, folk
4 different pets are kept: cat, chinchilla, goat, guinea-pig
1. the owner of the chinchilla is on the far left##1
2. the fan of d&b is between the owner of the cat and the fan of folk##2
3. the fan of folk is on the left of the fan of d&b##1
4. the fan of rock is on the far right##1
5. the fan of rock is on the right of the owner of the goat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop    | folk     | d&b | rock |
| Pet     | chinchilla | guinea-pig | goat       | cat     |

 